license: Apache-2.0
abstract: >-
  voiage provides Value of Information analysis through a hybrid Rust and
  Python implementation. Rust owns selected stable kernels and shared result
  contracts; Python owns the broader interface and method paths. R and Julia
  source packages currently expose direct EVPI bindings through the shared ABI.
keywords:
  - value of information
  - decision analysis
  - health economics
  - uncertainty quantification
